    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a \"crisis\" though. it feels permanent. like the world has already decided who i am now, and it's the person everyone hates. the person who failed. i try to imagine a future where things are okay, but i just see a blank wall. there's no Version 2.0 of me. there's just the wreckage.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
